Depletion (SSB relative to unfished SSB given current recruitment dynamics) for projected years 21-30 (a performance metrics function of class PM)

Depletion (SSB relative to unfished SSB given current recruitment dynamics) for projected years 21-30 (a performance metrics function of class PM)

D30

Arguments

MSE
An object of class MSE

Format

An object of class PM of length 1.

Value

a matrix with n Management procedures (MSE@nMP) and nsim (MSE@nsim) columns from MSE

Examples

loadABT()
#> ABT-MSE objects loaded
